{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"By those [winds] sent forth in succession,","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:2","price":"those that blow violently,","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:3","price":"and scatter [rainclouds] far and wide,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:4","price":"And by those [angels] who bring criterion[1];","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1] To Allah's messengers to distinguish between truth and falsehood.","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:5","price":"and those who deliver revelation,","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:6","price":"leaving no excuse or giving warning –","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:7","price":"what you are promised will surely come to pass.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:8","price":"So when the stars are effaced,","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:9","price":"and when the sky is split apart,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:10","price":"and when the mountains are blown away,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:11","price":"and when the messengers are summoned[2],","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[2] To testify concerning their nations.","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:12","price":"until which Day has all this been postponed?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:13","price":"Until the Day of Judgment.","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:14","price":"How do you know what the Day of Judgment is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:15","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers[3]!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[3] i.e., Death and destruction be upon them.","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:16","price":"Did We not destroy the earlier nations?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:17","price":"Then We will do likewise to the later ones.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:18","price":"This is how We deal with the wicked.","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:19","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:20","price":"Did We not create you from a worthless fluid,","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:21","price":"then We placed it in a secure repository","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:22","price":"for a determined period[4]?","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[4] See 23:12-14","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:23","price":"For We determined it; How excellently We determine!","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:24","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:25","price":"Have We not made the earth a receptacle[5]","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[5] i.e., a lodging, a container that contains all people.","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:26","price":"for the living and the dead,","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:27","price":"and placed therein firm towering mountains, and given you fresh water to drink?","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:28","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:29","price":"[They will be told,] “Proceed to that [Fire] which you used to deny!","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:30","price":"Proceed to the shadow [of smoke] ascending in three columns,","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:31","price":"that provides neither shade nor protection from the flames.","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:32","price":"Indeed, it [i.e., Hell] throws up sparks as big as castles,","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:33","price":"as if they were tawny camels[6].","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[6] i.e., huge and black camels.","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:34","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:35","price":"On that Day they won’t speak,","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:36","price":"nor will they be allowed to make excuses.","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:37","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:38","price":"[They will be told,] “This is the Day of Judgment: We have gathered you along with the earlier generations.","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:39","price":"So if you have any scheme, then plot it against Me.”","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:40","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:41","price":"Indeed, the righteous will be amid shades and springs","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:42","price":"and will have whatever fruit they desire.","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:43","price":"[They will be told,] “Eat and drink joyfully, as a reward for what you used to do.”","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:44","price":"This is how We reward those who do good.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:45","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:46","price":"“Eat and enjoy yourselves for a while; you are truly wicked.”","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:47","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:48","price":"When it is said to them, “Bow [in prayer],” they do not bow.","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:49","price":"Woe on that Day to the deniers!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"77:50","price":"In which message after this [Qur’an] will they believe?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}